text.tspan: Simply draw your tiles over this one, using it as a guide.

Do note that most of the tiles are simply mirrors of the others.
Tbere are only about 13 unique tiles. The rest are rotated copies.
If you do your editing in Inkscape, you can select a tile you suspect
to be a clone, and look at the bottom status bar. It should inform you
as to whether it is a clone or a group. If it's a clone, hit shift+d to lookup
the original. When you modify the original, the clones will update as well.
Keep in mind that tile positioning will change in the future.
Once I've gotten some feedback, I'll finalize their positions.
